cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with auto-annotation and semi-supervised learning, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of ensembles is also a common technique in both fields. The paper specifically focuses on semantic segmentation, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the use of quality filtering for auto-annotations could also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
